  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently when an incorrect/invalid response is given via the RPC, All peers associated with the chain are banned. \r\n\r\nCorrect handling of repairing the chain and isolating the malicious peer should be built. This makes sense to build once the network refactor (#664) is done such that the sync thread is handled correctly allowing the solution to not have to be re-written in the refactor. ",
